+## Overview
+
+Total revenue was $7,154.44 across 30 orders placed between 2026-05-02 and 2026-05-21. The median order value was $204.94.
+
+## Top Products
+
+Gadget led all products with $2,392.00 in revenue, about 33.4% of the total, from only 16 units sold. Widget followed at $2,118.94 (106 units), then Doohickey at $1,513.00 (17 units) and Sprocket at $1,130.50 (238 units). Sprocket moves the most units but earns the least revenue, reflecting its low $4.75 price.
+
+## Regional Performance
+
+North generated the most revenue at $2,176.35 from 8 orders. East followed with $1,830.79 (7 orders), South with $1,732.48 (8 orders), and West trailed at $1,414.82 (7 orders). North outperformed West by roughly 53.8%, a gap of $761.53.
+
+## Recommendations
+
+- Prioritize Gadget stock and promotions; it delivers a third of revenue from the fewest units sold.
+- Investigate West's weaker sales; it lags North by over half despite a similar order count.
+- Bundle Sprocket with higher-priced items to lift its low per-order revenue contribution.
